The Atlanta Braves and Ticketmaster would like to let you know about a fast and convenient way for you to pick up your Will Call tickets. venues.parkingDetail: There are a number of parking lots surrounding SunTrust Park for preferred, pre-paid and cash customers. It is recommended that guests arrive early and park in the first lot available to them. Guests should also check braves.com for parking updates in the Battery area. - BUS, LIMOUSINE & ALL OTHER OVERSIZED VEHICLE parking is available in Lot 17/18. There is a designated passenger drop-off location near the third-base gate. - DIAMOND PREFERRED, a valet assist program, is available on a pre-paid limited first come first served basis. Interested guests may contact the Membership Services Office at (404) 577-9100 for further information. - HANDICAPPED PARKING is available on a first-come, first-serve basis in all lots. Only vehicles with a valid, state issued disabled parking permit or license plate will be permitted to park in the disabled spaces. Parking at the Battery is managed by Laz Parking.

generalInfo.generalRule: Outside food and beverages, except for sealed plastic water bottles, are not allowed inside the gates of SunTrust Park on game days. However, guests can enjoy food and beverages from The Battery Atlanta outside in the plaza.

boxOfficeInfo.willCallDetail: HOURS : Opens 2 hrs prior to game time. The Atlanta Braves and Ticketmaster would like to let you know about a fast and convenient way for you to pick up your Will Call tickets. There are now 6 automated Will Call Kiosks located at SunTrust Park, near the 3rd Base Gate. To use the kiosks, simply insert the credit card you used to purchase your tickets for that day's game; your tickets will print automatically. PLEASE BRING A PICTURE ID, THE ACTUAL CREDIT CARD USED TO PURCHASE THE TICKETS, AND YOUR ORDER NUMBER.

venues.parkingDetail: There are a number of parking lots surrounding SunTrust Park for preferred, pre-paid and cash customers. It is recommended that guests arrive early and park in the first lot available to them. Guests should also check braves.com for parking updates in the Battery area. - BUS, LIMOUSINE & ALL OTHER OVERSIZED VEHICLE parking is available in Lot 17/18. There is a designated passenger drop-off location near the third-base gate. - DIAMOND PREFERRED, a valet assist program, is available on a pre-paid limited first come first served basis. Interested guests may contact the Membership Services Office at (404) 577-9100 for further information. - HANDICAPPED PARKING is available on a first-come, first-serve basis in all lots. Only vehicles with a valid, state issued disabled parking permit or license plate will be permitted to park in the disabled spaces. Parking at the Battery is managed by Laz Parking.
venues.accessibleSeatingDetail: SunTrust Park can accommodate all accessibilities Companion service animals are allowed in SunTrust Park.

generalInfo.generalRule: Outside food and beverages, except for sealed plastic water bottles, are not allowed inside the gates of SunTrust Park on game days. However, guests can enjoy food and beverages from The Battery Atlanta outside in the plaza.
generalInfo.childRule: Children 3 and older must have a ticket. Children under 3 are free on lap.
